# React Components

- Use functional components with typed props interfaces.
- Extract custom hooks when logic exceeds ~30 lines or is reused.
- Keep components ≤ ~300 lines; split UI into subcomponents by dialog/section.
- Side effects and API calls belong in hooks or services, not inline in JSX handlers.
- Use MUI components consistently; avoid inline styles when `sx` prop suffices.
- Redux: use `useAppSelector` / `useAppDispatch` from `src/store/hooks`.
- Auth in components: `useAuthData()`; never read Keycloak token directly in JSX.
